column1: # ITEMS DICTIONARY for ChatShop
# This file defines ChatShop's understanding of Minecraft items.
# Items not defined here will not be understood by ChatShop
# flatly refuse to interact with them.
# ChatShop does not support non-vanilla items.
# FORMAT:
# ID[:DMG]
# "minecraft:" omitted from all real_minecraft_names.
# ChatShop can query items by ID
# ALIASES:
# All references (in chat output) to items will be resolved to the first alias unless
# a !DISPLAY flag is present. Aliases which contain spaces will be logged twice; once with
# all spaces removed
column2: and once with all spaces replaced by underscores.

column1: # The !S flag is not yet implemented.
# Allowed flags:
#  !BAN           Items with this flag will be completely ignored. ChatShop will thusly refuse to
#                       interact with them at all. It is advised that you ban items rather than
#                       delete them
column2: in the interest of maintaining a complete dictionary.

column1: #  !DISPLAY-"..." The shop will use the specified display name instead of the first Alias
#  !S             The shop will not allow "s" forgiveness for this item.
#                       This flag is not yet implemented.
